@itschefjosej serving something special today for @uncorkforthecuresa chicharrón de ribeye fried in bone marrow al ajillo and roasted pine nuts. So excited to be here today!!

How are you loading your experience board?
We can plate most dishes on our menu in a board like you see above! It’s not one specific plate- you make your own!

Our family favorite (for 6 adults) is 1 lb of each meat, arrachera, sirloin, ribeye, salchicha asada, large guacamole, papa asada, quesadillitas, and extra ajo asado. Mind us we’ve already munched on appetizers like coliflor, empalmes, jalapeño poppers, and queso flameado. I know, we eat a lot 😅 but hey, we usually don’t have left overs.

Prime Picanha Barbacoa. What makes this barbacoa so special, you may ask. Our barbacoa is made from Picanha, a part from the cow that is very lean with a fat line outside the cut. Making this steak very flavorful without the grease marble that you would typically find in a ribeye, for example. 

We let the steak braise for 24 hours to get this shredded butter like presentation.

Most people make barbacoa with just cheek or tongue, that’s why our is considered PRIME BARBACOA, unlike others.

We serve it everyday from 8am until supplies last. Come try!!

AMAZING is the always the word of the day at @tuasador.satx 🤤 

This has become our special place to celebrate those beautiful moments in life. And we were blessed to have another beautiful moment last night with friends turned family. 😍

@tuasador.satx is not your ordinary steakhouse. This family owned and operated restaurant is a real Mexican Steakhouse that stays loyal to its Nuevo León roots. The flavors are out of bounds and everything is done so perfectly. When you’re looking for unique cuts of steak or something just flavored very differently, this is that place. 

We love the food so much but their drinks are truly spectacular. All the drinks are so vibrant and flavorful but never made with anything but fresh ingredients. No drink is overpriced and worth every sip. You will definitely find some unique concoctions that you just can’t find anywhere else in the city. That always makes for a fun night! 🍹 

Honestly, I could keep writing about this place, but you deserve to go and see for yourself. When you do go, make sure you tell ‘em Angel Food Dude sent ya! I did the same when @ohsoyouher.__ sent me! 🙏🏼 

Happy eating, SA! 😇

The @tuasador.satx Experience was the ULTIMATE Mexican steakhouse experience 🙌🏽🥩

This was my first time dining in a Mexican steakhouse, and I was blown away. The quality and consistency of all the cooking showed me that not only is everything bigger in Texas, it’s definitely better.

This J Webby sized platter would usually serve 10 people and featured an array of the @tuasador.satx signature favs including:
🔺38oz Tomahawk
🔺10oz Picanha
🔺12oz New York strip
🔺1 lb arrachera (skirt steak)
🔺1 lb sirloin
🔺.5lb Sausage
🔺Papa Asada loaded with bacon (potato)
🔺Empalmes de chicharrón
🔺5 corn quesadillas
🔺6 jalapeño poppers
🔺2 flour tortillas
🔺2 corn tortillas
🔺Mostachon de fresa 

I took my time on this one and enjoyed every single bite, polishing this off in 25mins 12secs.

Thank you to the @tuasador.satx team for having me, I’ll definitely be back next time I’m in Austin 🙌🏽
